text: David Ranibok Waiau Adeang (born 24 November 1969) is a Nauruan politician. In 2023, he became President of Nauru. He was the Speaker of the Parliament of Nauru, and Nauru's Minister of Finance and Justice. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Nauru Category:Current national leaders
title: David Adeang
